# Since Windows and Linux use different default line endings, Git may report a large number of modified files that have no differences aside from their line endings. To prevent this from happening, you can disable line ending conversion using a .gitattributes file
# See: (https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/devcontainers/tips-and-tricks#resolving-git-line-ending-issues-in-containers)
* text=auto eol=lf
*.{cmd,[cC][mM][dD]} text eol=crlf
*.{bat,[bB][aA][tT]} text eol=crlf